reviewText: This [film] was not interesting at all.  It was stupid and looked like a very cheap/unorganized documentary.  Let me be the example, DON'T waste your money, you will regret it.  I wish I could get a refund for BAD TASTE.  Back to the drawing board people.
A great movie that made you wonder what's next?  A small town  country setting with an original big old house.

This movie, while being a bit different, and obviously lower budget, is hilarious! And the story about Ashley Judd... Well, let's just say that I hope it's true, because it had me laughing for the entire rest of the movie.

Great cast, and really good acting! Definitely better than  the Paranormal Activity series.
